data.description: Discover the allure of this delightful 3-bedroom residence nestled in the corner lot of a tranquil cul-de-sac! It features a desert front yard and a 2-car garage with attached cabinets for extra storage. Be impressed by the immaculate open layout featuring tall ceilings and stylish tile flooring. The kitchen is a homemaker's dream, equipped with recessed lighting, ample wood cabinetry, a practical pantry, Corian counters, a mosaic tile backsplash, and a center island. Relax after a hard day's work in the sizeable primary bedroom, offering a dedicated bathroom and a walk-in closet. Out the back, you have a covered patio, pavers, artificial turf, and a hot tub to enjoy. Don't miss out!
